'''TshiVenḓa''' ndi luambo lu no ambiwa [[Afurika Tshipembe]]. Ndi luṅwe lwa dzinyambo dza tshiofisiri kha la Afrika Tshipembe. 

[[Phalaphala]] FM ndi tshititshi tsha radio tshi no hasha nga luambo lwa tshi-Venḓa.

